				<outline text="I confess I don’t care who wins the NBA finals." type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 02:19:21 GMT" tweetId="1413321846989234177" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413321846989234177" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
