				<outline text="The Delta Variant Isn't Just Hyper-Contagious. It Also Grows More Rapidly Inside You. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2021/07/08/1013794996/why-the-delta-variant-is-so-contagious-a-new-study-sheds-light&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 01:18:25 GMT" tweetId="1413306513372950528" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413306513372950528" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="Pfizer to ask FDA to authorize booster dose of COVID vaccine as Delta variant spreads. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/pfizer-ask-fda-authorize-booster-dose-covid-vaccine-delta-variant-spreads-2021-07-08/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 01:08:58 GMT" tweetId="1413304135525584898" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413304135525584898" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
				<outline text="I got a new Mac, an M1, with Big Sur. 

I want to use it to add music to my iPhone. 

The instructions say to look for it in the Finder's sidebar.

But it isn't there. 

Fully updated iPhone and Mac. 

Help?" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 21:58:23 GMT" tweetId="1413256173525118977" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413256173525118977" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" >
					<outline text="Apparently the problem was the cable. When I replaced it with a different cable the phone showed up in the sidebar. Thanks for all the suggestions." type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 22:59:48 GMT" tweetId="1413271629963091968" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413271629963091968" inReplyToId="1413256173525118977" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
