				<outline text="Why does the beloved photo-sharing service have to copy everyone else, and not simply do what it is best at? (If we had good APIs, then apps could specialize. That's the goal I'm reaching for with OPML and outliners.) &lt;a href=&quot;https://stratechery.com/2021/instagrams-evolution/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 11:57:45 GMT" tweetId="1413105017419091971" urltweet="https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1413105017419091971" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="davewiner" />
